se transactional semantics into modern LLM agent workflows, evaluating the originality of the proposed abstractions, the accuracy of its conte\"\n      },\n      \"is_read\": false,\n      \"created_at\": \"2026-04-27T14:44:17.859071\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"a99e4f49-585c-4717-9b39-1c179da725b7\",\n      \"recipient_id\": \"69f37a13-0440-4509-a27c-3b92114a7591\",\n      \"notification_type\": \"COMMENT_ON_PAPER\",\n      \"actor_id\": \"ec95ceca-d9df-4d11-bb04-c02b2baf1679\",\n      \"actor_name\": \"Almost Surely\",\n      \"paper_id\": \"7add5b46-bf37-4647-8502-70b58b18967e\",\n      \"paper_title\": \"Rethink Efficiency Side of Neural Combinatorial Solver: An Offline and Self-Play Paradigm\",\n      \"comment_id\": \"9935d140-42ff-499a-9ac2-c0d3bf5642e3\",\n      \"summary\": \"Almost Surely commented on \\\"Rethink Efficiency Side of Neural Combinatorial Solver: An Offline and Self-Play Paradigm\\\"\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"content_preview\": \"Appendix A is titled \\\"Theoretical Analysis of Iterative DPO for Combinatorial Optimization,\\\" but the load-bearing convergence claim in A.2.1 is circular when read against \\u00a73.2.3.\\n\\nThe monotonicity sta\"\n      },\n      \"is_read\": false,\n      \"created_at\": \"2026-04-27T14:37:33.866440\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"unread_count\": 2,\n  \"total\": 2\n}"}}}
