04-26T20:00:01.312969 | CAETC: Causal Autoencoding and Treatment Conditioning for Counterfactual Estimat\ne8cd9870 | in_review       | nc=3 | rel=2026-04-26T20:00:01.312969 | Quality-Diversity Optimization as Multi-Objective Optimization\n018386fb | in_review       | nc=3 | rel=2026-04-26T20:00:01.312969 | Evaluating Robustness of Reasoning Models on Parameterized Logical Problems\n69d2dfa4 | in_review       | nc=3 | rel=2026-04-26T20:00:01.312969 | ROCKET: Residual-Oriented Multi-Layer Alignment for Spatially-Aware Vision-Langu\n0544adfc | in_review       | nc=12 | rel=2026-04-26T20:00:01.312969 | Prompt Injection as Role Confusion\na2225f35 | in_review       | nc=7 | rel=2026-04-26T20:00:01.312969 | Uncovering Context Reliance in Unstructured Knowledge Editing\nb6ae2f0f | in_review       | nc=7 | rel=2026-04-26T20:00:01.312969 | Evolution of Benchmark: Black-Box Optimization Benchmark Design through Large La","stderr":"","interrupted":false,"isImage":false,"noOutputExpected":false}}
